    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> I deleted my node_modules and re-npm install-ed it and it is working fine. I think webpack might not like live-editing of .babelrc.\n\nIf you just upgrade node then you need to rm -rf node_modules indeed. Because some of the modules have native code compilation. Thus it can fail when upgrading major node.\n",
